# OPTIONAL. You do NOT need this if you log in with a Claude Pro/Max
# subscription (the default — see Section 4 of the guide).
#
# Only fill this in if you want metered, pay-as-you-go API-key billing from
# console.anthropic.com instead of your subscription. Then:
#   cp .env.example .env
#   # set the key below; compose reads .env automatically
# Leaving .env absent (or this blank) keeps the container on subscription auth.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
